<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>Viewport of the scene specifies at which portion of the render surface Qt3D is rendering to. Area outside the viewport is left untouched.</db:para>
</db:section>
<db:section xml:id="property-documentation">
<db:title>Property Documentation</db:title>
<db:section xml:id="normalizedRect-prop">
<db:title>normalizedRect : rect</db:title>
<db:para>Specifies the normalised rectangle for the viewport, i.e. the viewport rectangle is specified relative to the render surface size. Whole surface sized viewport is specified as [0.0, 0.0, 1.0, 1.0], which is the default.</db:para>
</db:section>
